          <p class="letter-spacing:1rem text:center mb:20 fade">競爭優勢</p>
          <p class="text:center mb:60 fade-up">僑威集團發揮競爭優勢並持續茁壯，成為全球客戶有電源應用需求時的首選合作夥伴</p>
          <div class="idx-capability-list-box img-full grid-cols:4@sm gap-x:45 mb:20@sm">
